<div id="Idea_3676"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3676-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3676">Utilize former Advisory Board Members&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6747-4049">bobby.lee</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Term limits for Board members have caused valuable input on federal issues to be lost.  Significant time is spent educating new members - long term members are often the most informed.  Create special avenues for former members to provide input, such as separate blogs, annual meetings, to tap into the time investment made into these citizens.</div>
