<div id="Idea_2498"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2498-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2498">A suggested structure for New Stratagies and Techniques&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3899-4049">johnbrose</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">It looks like the White House folks are thinking of incorporating Open Gevernment Dialogue into the formal structure of government. Good for them! </div>
